[I] Point and click selection of X11 font names

[T] The xfontsel application provides a simple way to display the fonts
[T] known to your X server, examine samples of each, and retrieve the X
[T] Logical Font Description full name for a font.

[U] https://www.X.org

[A] X.org Foundation {http://www.X.org}
